IMPORTANT — Third-party material and scope of this license
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
This benchmark is derived from MovieNet (Huang et al., ECCV 2020). The
CC BY-NC 4.0 license above covers ONLY the original material created by the
authors of this work, namely:
  * the screenplay-to-shot ALIGNMENT annotations (data/alignments/),
  * the subtitle-to-shot LINKAGE timing/metadata (data/linkages/), and
  * the toolkit, baselines, and documentation (src/, docs/).

It does NOT grant any rights to underlying copyrighted material that this
repository does not redistribute, including but not limited to:
  * verbatim screenplay text,
  * movie subtitles,
  * movie poster images, and
  * movie frames / keyframes.

Those assets remain the property of their respective rights holders. They are
NOT included in this repository and must be obtained by the user from
MovieNet (and other original sources) under those sources' own licenses and
terms of use. See data/README.md for instructions on regenerating them
locally. By using this benchmark you agree to comply with the terms of
MovieNet and of the original rights holders.

When citing this benchmark, please also cite MovieNet (see CITATION.cff).
